  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed change of use by virtue of the loss of industrial floorspace and resulting retail/public space which would not be ancillary, would have a detrimental impact on the Locally Significant Industrial Site (LSIS) contrary to policies LP26 &#x27;Employment Land and Floorspace&#x27; and LP28 &#x27;&amp;nbsp;Protecting and Promoting Industrial Land and Floorspace in the Borough&#x27; of the LP33.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;Insufficient information was submitted regarding transport issues and servicing including use of the site by delivery drivers to allow the Local Planning Authority to assess whether the proposed change of use is suitable for the site without detriment to neighbouring residential amenity and highway and pedestrian safety contrary to policies LP2 (Development and Amenity) and LP43 (Transport and Development) of LP33 (2020), policies T4 (Assessing and mitigating transport impacts), T5 (Cycling) and T7 (Deliveries, servicing and construction) of London Plan (2021).&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
